<lb/> having plenty of snow this week, hence the value of 
<lb/> warm clothing. I earnestly trust Your Ladyship 
<lb/> will accept this card as all the gratitude which 
<lb/> a grateful prisoner can show again thanking Your 
<lb/> Ladyship.</p> <salute>I am Gratefully Yours</salute>
<signed>Pte Aidan Nolan</signed>
        
    

    
         
